{{ bar_chart }} Welcome to the <b>Server Monitoring Dashboard</b>!

Here you can track essential server metrics:
{{ chart_increasing }} CPU Usage
{{ chart_decreasing }} Memory Consumption
{{ hard_drive }} Disk Space
{{ thermometer }} Temperature

{% if available_periods -%}
{{ calendar }} <b>Available Statistics Periods:</b>
